data.description: Just reduced....This condo is in a great location close to the interstate and shopping only 15 minutes to Downtown restaurants and Live music. The seller recently installed new LVP flooring throughout the whole house. If you need lots of room but very little maintenance this place is for you. The condo association maintains the yard and common areas. All the kitchen appliances remain. The AC Unit was just installed at the end of June 2023. Selling as-is We need 24 hours' notice to show. Cannot show on Saturdays.
